{"tid":1615523,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"［正名］將和理非同勇武都改口叫「行動派」","createTime":"2019-10-03T06:25:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-08T04:24:42.000Z","uid":24465,"like":25,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"14ac24b140cdcedbff16f99cf7b80e731ebb3c13","tid":1615523,"uid":24465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T06:25:11.000Z","msg":"自抗爭以嚟已經有唔少post講過<br />\n和理非同勇武依兩個term 會令人自動歸邊<br />\n依度唔詳講 <br />\n個post其實都係主要針對只做「和理非」行動嘅手足<br />\n<br />\n時至今日 <br />\n仍然有唔少「和理非」<br />\n仲係<br />\n開住ig post圍爐話好嬲好嬲<br />\n食住美心藍店<br />\n繼續返工返學<br />\n<br />\n我諗咗好耐 <br />\n究竟有咩方法可以令佢地行多步<br />\n最後都係開post講下我嘅諗法<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>所有真香港人 <br />\n都應該叫自己做行動派</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n日五罷買 係行動<br />\n杯葛藍店支持黃店 係行動<br />\n罷工罷課 係行動<br />\n參加集會遊行人鏈 係行動<br />\n加入Twitter國際戰線 係行動<br />\nAirdrop文宣 係行動<br />\n捐錢 係行動<br />\n做家長 係行動<br />\n去商場唱歌10點嗌口號 都係行動<br />\n<br />\n上面嘅<br />\n全部都係「勇武」同「和理非」都做到嘅行動<br />\n<br />\n要令和理非升級 就一定要逼到佢地<strong>行動</strong><br />\n就算唔上前線都要知道<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">和勇不分 並唔係口號<br />\n而係行動</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n上前線 中後排 滅火 係行動<br />\n麻包袋 係行動<br />\n獅鳥 係行動<br />\n火魔法 係行動<br />\n打狗救人 都係行動<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔係話和理非為前線冇付出<br />\n但大家都知前線手足為我地付出嘅 <br />\n我地遠遠報答唔到<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n從今日起<br />\n你要配得起<strong>真香港人</strong>嘅身份<br />\n你就要做貼地嘅行動<br />\nig facebook發post嘅行動 <br />\n可以令你喺圈子入面宣洩不滿<br />\n但加入國際戰線嘅行動<br />\n可以令全世界嘅人同你一齊不滿<br />\n一齊對抗 黑警 港共 CCP 極權<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>所有香港人<br />\n請叫自己做行動派</strong></span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n我重申<br />\n<br />\n<strong>日五罷買 係行動<br />\n杯葛藍店支持黃店 係行動<br />\n罷工罷課 係行動<br />\n參加集會遊行人鏈 係行動<br />\n加入Twitter國際戰線 係行動<br />\nAirdrop文宣 係行動<br />\n捐錢 係行動<br />\n做家長 係行動<br />\n去商場唱歌10點嗌口號 都係行動</strong><br />\n<br />\n和理非行動嘅手足 勇武嘅手足<br />\n我地一齊行動 好唔好？<br />\n<br />\n同意嘅<br />\n就幫我大大力推上去<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"e3f37d8f6a11e53ffcb8f171b454c2ce0e91e74d","tid":1615523,"uid":24465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T06:26:49.000Z","msg":"你可以話自己嘅取向係和理非或者勇武<br />\n<br />\n但你必須實際行動<br />\n先配得起香港人依個名"},{"pid":"a5cd593744269bad1b2f7532da86f1ba5d417289","tid":1615523,"uid":24465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T06:27:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NGNSfxa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNGNSfxa.jpg&h=acafeb4e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c9aaf85ed4bb6663898b979397cb5aa15c33a907","tid":1615523,"uid":89974,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T06:28:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />分行動派同吹水派"},{"pid":"e66b48daea6cc33fbe650f85e90a877b314e03b7","tid":1615523,"uid":124910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T06:28:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fa5646b237e643293eac93c5fc6e7bce393f6ee","tid":1615523,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T06:28:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ea099d1baa0a205cc5af8ef2644d7a5d58b83e5","tid":1615523,"uid":24465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c9aaf85ed4bb6663898b979397cb5aa15c33a907","tid":1615523,"uid":89974,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T06:28:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />分行動派同吹水派"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T06:28:41.000Z","msg":"啱"},{"pid":"ce0cf3bb86ab03047774c646de3268081972d809","tid":1615523,"uid":64120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T06:29:45.000Z","msg":"講得好"},{"pid"